SimpleCommunication: Changelog (CHANGES)
----------------------------------------

Update 0
========

    Revision 2 (09/09/2017)
    -----------------------
- docs              :   now archived into a ZIP file
- ClientSocket
- ServerSocket      :   fixed bug at readQuery where buffer is still parsed even
                        if empty
- ServerPresenter   :   restyled console logs
- ServerPresenter   :   blocking of new clients if fully occupied
- ServerPresenter   :   now does client kicking independently
- ClientObject
- ServerPresenter   :   new spam protection
- ClientPresenter   :   now handles audio service absence
- GDMAudioEngine    :   updated to u0r2

    Revision 1 (08/30/2017)
    -----------------------
- docs              :   near-complete documentation with corrections
- ServerPresenter   :   added "Administrator", "Admin" to KEYWORDS
- ServerPresenter   :   names with whitespaces are now disallowed
- ClientPresenter   :   removed REGEX_EOT, unused constant
- GDMAudio
- GDMAudioEngine    :   updated to u0r1

    Revision 0 (08/22/2017)
    -----------------------
- initial release
